                    <h2 id="endpoints-POSTapi-google-webhook">Handle incoming Google Ads Lead Form webhook.</h2>

<p>
</p>

<p>Google sends a POST request with the lead data.
Verification is done via the 'google-key' header or 'google_key' payload field matched against our database.</p>

<span id="example-requests-POSTapi-google-webhook">
<blockquote>Example request:</blockquote>


<div class="bash-example">
    <pre><code class="language-bash">curl --request POST \
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/google/webhook" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
