                    <h2 id="endpoints-POSTapi-leads-duplicates-bulk-action">Bulk actions for duplicate leads (stored inside leads table).</h2>

<p>
</p>

<p>Actions:</p>
<ul>
<li>resolve_keep_original: deletes the duplicate lead and keeps original (uses meta_data.duplicate_of).</li>
<li>enable_duplicate: converts duplicate lead into a normal lead (clears duplicate flags/link).</li>
<li>transfer: assigns the duplicate lead to a new sales person (requires sales_id).</li>
<li>warn: sends notification about duplicates (uses meta_data.duplicate_of if original_lead_id not provided).</li>
